  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "Provide technical support with team of legal and gender expert to the MoWCSW to organise inclusive consultations for finalizing new laws on Gender equality (taking an instersectionality approach) : violence against women bill and special opportunity bill in line with the new Constitution and the Political Declaration adopted at CSW 59 \r\n\r\nSupport Government training institutions to integrate GE provisions (including GRB) in their training curriculum and provide trainings to further enhance capacities of Government officials in line with the SDGs \r\n\r\nSupport to LGCDP Joint Financing Agreement\r\n\r\nProvide technical support to the National Women’s Commission to monitor the implementation of UPR and CEDAW recommendation. \r\nOrganize national and district level trainings to the government officials and CSOs on national and international human rights instruments - CEDAW, Beijing + 20 and UPR"
    },
    "ne": null
  },
